766
00:42:32,409 --> 00:42:33,769
Do you think

767
00:42:33,769 --> 00:42:36,250
Men Sandao has more clues?

768
00:42:38,610 --> 00:42:41,250
So you need to get all the clues

769
00:42:41,690 --> 00:42:45,289
